High school roundup (Oct. 20) 
Tuesday's high school sports news. Photospin.com Order Reprint of this Story Volleyball 
(At) Carolina Forest 3, Sumter 0: Ellissa Small had 15 kills and Julie McKinney had 23 assists and seven service points as the Panthers won 25-13, 25-6, 25-6. 
Kenzlie Andresen added 18 service points and Sam Maxim had 14 straight service points for Carolina Forest. Related content
